title: ImagineFX Presents - The Digital Artist's Survival Guide
description:
ImagineFX Presents - The Digital Artist's Survival Guide

116 Pages | True PDF | English | 22 MB 


Learn the fundamentals of digital art! Over 100 bite-sized chunks of art advice and inspiration covering character and envrionment painting, vehicle and creature design. Plus, get started in core software, including Photoshop, Corel Painter and Sketchbook Pro.
